# Clean Architecture Boundaries

- Domain layer does not depend on Infrastructure.
- Application layer depends on Domain abstractions only.
- Infrastructure implements ports/interfaces defined by Application/Domain.
- Web/API layer orchestrates requests and delegates use-case execution.

## Dependency rule

Only depend inward:

`Web -> Application -> Domain`
